{"tid":317542,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人錄自己瞓覺?","createTime":"2017-07-11T13:40:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-11T13:44:58.000Z","uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"58b38cd64310c6abf4626bf7599ac53fa3bced07","tid":317542,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:40:53.000Z","msg":"是咁的，早一兩個月開始，朝朝起身都發覺隻手痴笠笠，個口又一陣甜味，以為夢遊用手食雪糕，冇乜點理。<br />\n<br />\n到上個星期開始起身對腳有泥，忍唔住想錄低自己瞓覺果時做過啲咩野，就用部舊相機set 好腳架影自己瞓覺，結果發現左好詭異既事...."},{"pid":"249c6a7a38cc30c526c22c550b7e2dec3f1e7007","tid":317542,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:42:07.000Z","msg":"我平時兩點鐘瞓，通常幾分鐘內就會瞓著，條片一開頭15分鐘好靜，到17左右就有啲二胡聲..."},{"pid":"d0cb3acc14721c607f7e28b7323902877da07f7f","tid":317542,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:42:59.000Z","msg":"做嘜鳩啊你 買左餸未呀"},{"pid":"0570f804c0667b75ff46815b25c050f84f3edc2e","tid":317542,"uid":47480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>做嘜鳩啊你 買左餸未呀</blockquote><br />\n喂 街市收6點呀 遲左連鳩毛都冇你買呀"},{"pid":"680a4339646b19580855273bb986f9cb716b1401","tid":317542,"uid":74824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-11T13:44:58.000Z","msg":"奸奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"}]}